Nigerian socialite and entrepreneur, Obinna Iyiegbu, popularly known as Obi Cubana, has gifted 20 of his struggling classmates at Dennis Memorial Grammar School Onitsha, N40m to be shared among them. He disclosed this while speaking at the high school reunion party on Friday in Abuja, urging some of his classmates to top his donation in order to assist the poor ones among them. The reunion which was hosted by the billionaire businessman to celebrate their 30 years of leaving high school. His caption in a post on his official Instagram page read, “My Secondary School classmates are here!! The DMGS C92 Reunion 2022, 30yrs after!! Glad to have u guys around. Let’s have maximum fun!”